commands.name: vertex
commands.command: apt update -y && apt upgrade -y && apt install curl -y && curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh && sh get-docker.sh && timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Shanghai && mkdir -p /root/vertex && chmod 777 /root/vertex && docker run -d --name vertex --restart unless-stopped --network host -v /root/vertex:/vertex -e TZ=Asia/Shanghai lswl/vertex:stable
